<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Your Trial is Ending Soon - Wonderful Books</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'Roboto', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 0;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6600 0%, #ff8533 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
        }
        .header p {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        .highlight-box {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .highlight-box .days-left {
            font-size: 36px;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #ff6600;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
        }
        .highlight-box .trial-end {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #856404;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .cta-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff6600 0%, #ff8533 100%);
            color: white !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 25px;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            transition: transform 0.2s ease;
        }
        .cta-button:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }
        .benefits {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin: 25px 0;
        }
        .benefits h3 {
            color: #ff6600;
            margin: 0 0 15px 0;
            font-size: 20px;
        }
        .benefits ul {
            margin: 0;
            padding-left: 20px;
        }
        .benefits li {
            margin: 8px 0;
            color: #555;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 25px 30px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            border-top: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #ff6600;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .social-links {
            margin: 15px 0;
        }
        .social-links a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 0 10px;
            color: #999;
            font-size: 18px;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0 10px;
                border-radius: 0;
            }
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 25px 20px;
            }
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            .highlight-box .days-left {
                font-size: 28px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>üìö Wonderful Books</h1>
            <p>Your premium reading experience</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hi <%= firstName %>,</h2>
            
            <p>We hope you've been enjoying your free trial of Wonderful Books! We wanted to give you a friendly reminder that your trial is coming to an end soon.</p>
            
            <div class="highlight-box">
                <div class="days-left"><%= daysLeft %> day<%= daysLeft !== 1 ? 's' : '' %></div>
                <p class="trial-end">left in your free trial (ends <%= trialEndDate %>)</p>
            </div>
            
            <p style="text-align: center;">
                <strong>Don't let your reading journey end here!</strong><br>
                Upgrade now to continue accessing our entire library of transformational books.
            </p>
            
            <div style="text-align: center;">
                <a href="<%= upgradeUrl %>" class="cta-button">Continue Reading - Upgrade Now</a>
            </div>
            
            <div class="benefits">
                <h3>üåü Why upgrade to Premium?</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Unlimited Access</strong> - Read as many books as you want</li>
                    <li><strong>Exclusive Content</strong> - Access to premium titles and new releases</li>
                    <li><strong>Advanced Features</strong> - Bookmarks, progress sync, and more</li>
                    <li><strong>Ad-Free Experience</strong> - Focus on what matters: your growth</li>
                    <li><strong>Support Authors</strong> - Help us bring you more amazing content</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p>We believe in the power of books to transform lives, and we'd love to continue being part of your journey.</p>
            
            <p>If you have any questions about upgrading or need help with anything, just reply to this email - we're here to help!</p>
            
            <p>Happy reading,<br>
            <strong>The Wonderful Books Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>
                <strong>Wonderful Books</strong><br>
                Transforming lives through the power of reading
            </p>
            
            <div class="social-links">
                <a href="#">üìß</a>
                <a href="#">üåê</a>
                <a href="#">üì±</a>
            </div>
            
            <p>
                You're receiving this email because you have an active trial with us.<br>
                <a href="<%= unsubscribeUrl %>">Unsubscribe</a> | 
                <a href="mailto:books@thekingdomclub.org">Contact Support</a>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>